ezvcard.util
Class TreeMultimap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
  ezvcard.util.TreeMultimap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the key
V - the value
public class TreeMultimap<K,V>
extends Object

A multimap that uses Set objects to store its values.

The internal Map implementation is a TreeMap that uses TreeSet for its values.

Author:
Michael Angstadt
